    "Moreover, long-form decoding significantly narrowed the gap, decreasing the word error rate for both EPTV and ITV.",
    "Meanwhile, our ASR shows the best performance for Peloton without any modifications.",
    "Additionally, we evaluated Seamless to assess its robustness and found that its performance was severely lacking in comparison.",
    "Based on these results, we use the ASR with standard segmentation for TED and Peloton test sets.",
    "For EPTV and ITV, we use the ASR system with long-form decoding."
